---
// Página de producto: VClub
import MainLayout from '../../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
---

<MainLayout 
  title="VClub | Streaming sin Límites - Digital-X"
  description="VClub es tu puerta al entretenimiento. Suscripción de streaming con créditos para múltiples plataformas. Disfruta de contenido ilimitado."
>
  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="relative min-h-[70vh] flex items-center pt-24 overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[var(--color-bg-dark)]">
      <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-20" style="background-image: linear-gradient(rgba(0, 217, 255, 0.1) 1px, transparent 1px), linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(0, 217, 255, 0.1) 1px, transparent 1px); background-size: 50px 50px;"></div>
      <div class="absolute top-1/4 right-1/4 w-[600px] h-[600px] bg-[var(--color-secondary)] rounded-full filter blur-[200px] opacity-20"></div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="container-custom relative z-10">
      <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
        <div>
          <nav class="flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-[var(--color-text-muted)] mb-8">
            <a href="/" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">Inicio</a>
            <span>/</span>
            <a href="/#productos" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">Productos</a>
            <span>/</span>
            <span class="text-[var(--color-secondary)]">VClub</span>
          </nav>
          
          <h1 class="heading-xl mb-6">
            <span class="text-[var(--color-secondary)]">V</span><span class="text-white">Club</span>
          </h1>
          
          <p class="text-xl text-[var(--color-text-secondary)] mb-8 leading-relaxed">
            Tu streaming, tus reglas. Una suscripción con créditos para acceder a 
            <span class="text-white font-semibold">múltiples plataformas</span> de entretenimiento.
          </p>
          
          <div class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-4 mb-8">
            <div class="text-center p-4 rounded-xl bg-white/5 border border-white/10">
              <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-[var(--color-secondary)]">10+</div>
              <div class="text-xs text-[var(--color-text-muted)]">Plataformas</div>
            </div>
            <div class="text-center p-4 rounded-xl bg-white/5 border border-white/10">
              <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-[var(--color-secondary)]">∞</div>
              <div class="text-xs text-[var(--color-text-muted)]">Contenido</div>
            </div>
            <div class="text-center p-4 rounded-xl bg-white/5 border border-white/10">
              <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-[var(--color-secondary)]">1</div>
              <div class="text-xs text-[var(--color-text-muted)]">Suscripción</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4">
            <a href="#video" class="btn-primary" style="background: var(--color-secondary);">
              Ver demo
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" class="ml-2">
                <polygon points="5 3 19 12 5 21 5 3"></polygon>
              </svg>
            </a>
            <a href="/#contacto" class="btn-secondary">
              Solicitar información
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="relative flex items-center justify-center">
          <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[var(--color-secondary)] rounded-full filter blur-[100px] opacity-30 animate-pulse"></div>
          <div class="relative w-64 h-64 md:w-80 md:h-80 rounded-3xl bg-gradient-to-br from-[var(--color-secondary)] to-[var(--color-primary)] flex items-center justify-center shadow-2xl">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="100" height="100" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="white" stroke-width="2">
              <polygon points="5 3 19 12 5 21 5 3"></polygon>
            </svg>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  
  <!-- Características -->
  <section class="section-padding bg-[var(--color-bg-darker)]">
    <div class="container-custom">
      <div class="text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-16">
        <h2 class="heading-lg mb-4">¿Cómo funciona <span class="text-[var(--color-secondary)]">VClub</span>?</h2>
        <p class="text-[var(--color-text-secondary)]">
          Un sistema revolucionario de créditos que te da libertad total para elegir qué ver y dónde verlo.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <div class="card text-center">
          <div class="w-20 h-20 mx-auto mb-6 rounded-full bg-[var(--color-secondary)]/10 flex items-center justify-center">
            <span class="text-3xl font-bold text-[var(--color-secondary)]">1</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3">Suscríbete</h3>
          <p class="text-[var(--color-text-secondary)]">
            Elige el plan que mejor se adapte a tus necesidades de entretenimiento.
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="card text-center">
          <div class="w-20 h-20 mx-auto mb-6 rounded-full bg-[var(--color-secondary)]/10 flex items-center justify-center">
            <span class="text-3xl font-bold text-[var(--color-secondary)]">2</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3">Recibe Créditos</h3>
          <p class="text-[var(--color-text-secondary)]">
            Obtén créditos mensuales para usar en las plataformas de tu preferencia.
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="card text-center">
          <div class="w-20 h-20 mx-auto mb-6 rounded-full bg-[var(--color-secondary)]/10 flex items-center justify-center">
            <span class="text-3xl font-bold text-[var(--color-secondary)]">3</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3">Disfruta</h3>
          <p class="text-[var(--color-text-secondary)]">
            Canjea tus créditos y accede a contenido ilimitado en múltiples plataformas.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  
  <!-- Video -->
  <section id="video" class="section-padding">
    <div class="container-custom">
      <div class="text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-12">
        <h2 class="heading-lg mb-4"><span class="text-[var(--color-secondary)]">VClub</span> en acción</h2>
      </div>
      
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <div class="relative group">
          <div class="absolute -inset-4 bg-[var(--color-secondary)] rounded-3xl opacity-20 blur-xl"></div>
          <div class="relative glass rounded-2xl overflow-hidden">
            <div class="aspect-video">
              <iframe
                src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/mCBQKuIoVCo?rel=0&modestbranding=1"
                title="VClub Demo"
                frameborder="0"
                allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share"
                allowfullscreen
                class="w-full h-full"
                loading="lazy"
              ></iframe>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  
  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="section-padding bg-[var(--color-bg-darker)]">
    <div class="container-custom">
      <div class="card p-12 text-center relative overflow-hidden">
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[var(--color-secondary)]/10"></div>
        <div class="relative z-10">
          <h2 class="heading-lg mb-4">¿Listo para el entretenimiento sin límites?</h2>
          <p class="text-[var(--color-text-secondary)] mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
            Únete a VClub y descubre una nueva forma de disfrutar el streaming.
          </p>
          <a href="/#contacto" class="btn-primary inline-flex" style="background: var(--color-secondary);">
            Solicitar información
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</MainLayout>
